title: The Nipi Cooler's creator talks rapid prototyping with 3D printing at TCT Show
text:
The Nipi Cooler's creator talks rapid prototyping with 3D printing at TCT Show 20 October 2015 Expand Luke Guttery at TCT Show Creator of the much lauded Nipi Cooler , Luke Guttery, takes to the TCT Show stage to discuss the benefits of 3D printing for rapid prototyping and design. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
